{"tid":817514,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"林俊傑扮蠟像嚇周杰倫","createTime":"2018-09-13T11:59:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-14T04:13:13.000Z","uid":160977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c6abf279db95561cd2fd99c740dad9bc1dcf6622","tid":817514,"uid":160977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T11:59:21.000Z","msg":"林俊傑JJ在香港的演唱會，一票難求，大家都撲飛，其實JJ唱得外，亦好玩得，好似開騷在後台化妝，會突然嚇吓化妝師，搞吓氣氛；今次，他就扮蠟像嚇周杰倫。<br />\n<br />\n周杰倫走去蠟像館睇吓自己的蠟像，就同大家講每一處自己的蠟像都有少少不一樣，在衣著及打扮上都有分別，然後又行去旁邊介紹林俊傑的蠟像，又叫攝影師行埋一點，他要跟林俊傑的蠟像比一比誰的眼晴比較大喎！就在此時，林俊傑的蠟像郁一郁作狀撲前，然後唱咗幾句歌，嚇到周杰倫後退，原來林俊傑蠟像係真人，JJ仲搞笑話，「周杰倫被嚇時，那驚嚇程度的眼晴比較大！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2xaNPa5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2xaNPa5&d=ARVbjqz86EcL4jQg4C3lVv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=e5c806c5\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2xaNPa5</a>"},{"pid":"7d871168226fcb478adf0afb5f3bff33ed03a9f8","tid":817514,"uid":208726,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T12:01:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3878b9f84369fd1ce3cc592b6f3be01b19be0711","tid":817514,"uid":190383,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T12:03:28.000Z","msg":"似夾定喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1145de253ee4f17791ae3a243d44b03e0af7bfa3","tid":817514,"uid":35746,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T12:06:15.000Z","msg":"假到"},{"pid":"2df89bc6083341034e5312713d4af357a5ea2e97","tid":817514,"uid":124935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T03:44:36.000Z","msg":"留意枝咪"},{"pid":"ca2021e3fc0b4510eb00e3d0c4d0d013dd23e618","tid":817514,"uid":33668,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1145de253ee4f17791ae3a243d44b03e0af7bfa3","tid":817514,"uid":35746,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T12:06:15.000Z","msg":"假到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T03:47:21.000Z","msg":"奶共後轉咗隊合蚹帼情的PR...就搞成咁喇<br />\n<br />\nBTW 計得交稅呀<img src=\